A simple client/server whiteboard app using WebSockets.
Run the server, connect through your browser.

Server usage:
  ruby server/server_2.rb <port>

(You can use the old server, which supports fewer features: ruby server/server.rb <port>)

Client usage:
  open index.html in your browser, type the address and port and click connect

Proof that it works: see <IT_WORKS.png>

